# 🗂 Dataset Information

The dataset contains transactional records of an e-commerce business.

### Dataset Includes

| Column   | Description          |
| -------- | -------------------- |
| Order ID | Unique order number  |
| Product  | Product Name         |
| Category | Product Category     |
| City     | Customer City        |
| Region   | Sales Region         |
| Sales    | Revenue generated    |
| Quantity | Number of items sold |
| Profit   | Profit earned        |
| Date     | Order Date           |

